  <original-body>When we set name to state machine, dynamic method of current state falls.

Example:

class Example
  include ActiveModel::StateMachine
  state_machine :example do
    state :new
    state :changed

    event :change do
      transitions :from =&gt; :new, :to =&gt; :changed
    end
  end
end

p = Example.new
p.change!
p.current_state(:example) # =&gt; :changed
p.changed? # =&gt; :new</original-body>
